---
// "Not all therapists are created equal" — vetting + founder image
---
<section style="background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--paper-3) 0%,var(--paper-2) 52%,var(--sand-2) 100%);padding:72px 36px;" class="pad-fluid">
  <div class="split" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--forest-mid),var(--forest));border-radius:24px;padding:56px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.1fr .9fr;gap:48px;align-items:center;color:var(--cream-text);box-shadow:0 18px 64px -24px rgba(33,58,48,.4);">
    <div>
      <h2 class="h2-fluid" style="font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:500;font-size:40px;line-height:1.1;margin:0 0 14px;color:var(--white);">Not all therapists are created equal.</h2>
      <p style="font-size:17.5px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--sage-pale);margin:0 0 28px;">Exceptional therapy requires exceptional humans. We accept less than 1% of applicants — selecting, from a deep pool of master's-level clinicians, only the rare blend of intelligence, training, self-awareness, and presence that produces truly life-changing results.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:32px;">
        <div><div style="font-family:var(--serif);font-size:30px;color:var(--white);">&lt;1%</div><div style="font-size:13.5px;color:var(--sage-pale-2);">acceptance rate</div></div>
        <div><div style="font-family:var(--serif);font-size:30px;color:var(--white);">100%</div><div style="font-size:13.5px;color:var(--sage-pale-2);">master's-level &amp; vetted</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="aspect-ratio:1;border-radius:18px;background:linear-gradient(150deg,var(--forest-soft),var(--sage));position:relative;overflow:hidden;">
      <img src="/images/founder-brooke.webp" alt="Founder Brooke Sprowl — every My LA Therapy therapist is personally vetted and trained" style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center top;" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
